# Source roadmap

When adding new connectors:
1) Consult @docs/sources_backlog.md
2) Add/modify sources.toml entries
3) Implement the connector module
4) Add a non-network unit test for parsing/normalization
5) Run end-to-end ingest once + show-latest

If the @docs include doesn’t work, open docs/sources_backlog.md and attach it explicitly in chat.
